author: Alex Frangos
title: China’s Battered Economy Could Surprise Investors
text:
China’s economic data of late rarely disappoints in one respect: providing headlines about growth being the slowest in years.
China’s growth obviously just isn’t what it used to be. The main question for investors now is if the economy is cracking apart completely.
